Symbol.Script_3D:
!-----------3d--------------------- if show_el < EPS then end IF gs_detlevel_3D_m < EPS THEN END CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL one_ConID=0 returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, sMat, gs_InsMat, MEP_cline_pen, show_el
! Steam Air Curtain
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
unID = 1 IF mbShow THEN ! --- HOTSPOTS --- !
HOTSPOT A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -B/2+B*(wrate01+wrate02), 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -B/2+B*(wrate01+wrate02), 0, unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT A/2, B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX*hrate, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -A/2, -B/2, ZZYZX*hrate, unID: unID=unID+1
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
ROTy -90 ADD 0, -B/2, -A/2 IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN GROUP "mainbox" PRISM_ 7, A, 0, B, 15, ZZYZX, B, 15, ZZYZX, 0, 15, ZZYZX*hrate, 0, 15, ZZYZX*hrate, B*wrate01, 15, 0, B*(wrate01+wrate02), 15, 0, B, -1 ENDGROUP
GROUP "boxes" num = INT(A/0.25) boxDist = (A-0.05*num)/num+0.05 FOR i = 1 TO num ADD ZZYZX*hrate+0.025, 0, 0.025+boxDist*(i-1) BLOCK ZZYZX*(1-hrate)-0.05, 0.025, boxDist-0.05 DEL 1 NEXT i ENDGROUP
result = SUBGROUP("mainbox","boxes") PLACEGROUP result
KILLGROUP "mainbox" KILLGROUP "boxes"
FOR i = 1 TO num ADDz boxDist*(i-1) numH = 3 distH = (boxDist-0.05)/(numH+1) FOR j = 1 TO numH ADD ZZYZX*hrate+0.025, 0, 0.025+distH*j RECT ZZYZX*(1-hrate)-0.05, 0.025 DEL 1 NEXT j
numV = INT((ZZYZX*(1-hrate)-0.05)/0.045)-1 IF numV < EPS THEN numV = 1 distV = (ZZYZX*(1-hrate)-0.05)/(numV+1) FOR j = 1 TO numV ADD ZZYZX*hrate+0.025+distV*j, 0, 0.025 ROTy -90 RECT boxDist-0.05, 0.025 DEL 2 NEXT j DEL 1 NEXT i ELSE PRISM_ 7, A, 0, B, 15, ZZYZX, B, 15, ZZYZX, 0, 15, ZZYZX*hrate, 0, 15, ZZYZX*hrate, B*wrate01, 15, 0, B*(wrate01+wrate02), 15, 0, B, -1 ENDIF DEL 2 ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 17, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConPosZ_2=ConPosZ_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConEdit_2 = 17, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData END
Symbol.Script_2D:
!-----------2d--------------------- if show_el < EPS then end IF gs_detlevel_2D_m < EPS THEN END CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL one_ConID=0 returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, MEP_cline_type, MEP_cline_pen, show_el
! Steam Air Curtain
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- MAIN BOX --- !
HOTSPOT2 A/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1
PUT A/2, B/2, 1, -A/2, B/2, 1, -A/2, -B/2, 1, A/2, -B/2, 1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
SET FILL gs_fill_type
PEN gs_cont_pen IF gs_fill_pen THEN PEN gs_fill_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 3+32, 4, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1, mbShow = 0 PEN gs_cont_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 2, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1, mbShow = 0 ENDIF
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 -SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED))+SYMB_ROTANGLE * (DrawingNum > 1 AND SYMB_MIRRORED)
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180*NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConShow_1 = 0, ConEdit_1 = 13, ConPosX_2=ConPosX_2, ConPosY_2=ConPosY_2, ConLength_2=ConLength_2, ConShow_2 = 0, ConEdit_2 = 13, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData DEL 1
END

! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF A < 0.30 THEN A = 0.30 VALUES "A" RANGE [0.30, ] IF B < 0.12 THEN B = 0.12 VALUES "B" RANGE [0.12, ] IF ZZYZX < 0.12 THEN ZZYZX = 0.12 VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [0.12, ] ENDIF

CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"

ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_2, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_2, ConWidth = ConWidth_2, ConDepth = ConDepth_2, ConLength = ConLength_2, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_2, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_2, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_2, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_2, ConToolType = ConToolType_2, ConStatus = ConStatus_2, ConType_2 = ConType_2, ConConnectorType_2 = ConConnectorType_2, ConSystem_2 = ConSystem_2, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
